---
description: Enforce approval and escalation guardrails for high-risk AI agent actions
alwaysApply: true
globs:
  - "**/*"
---

High-risk actions must be human-governed.

- Risky tools require approval (`requiresApproval: true`).
- Define escalation behavior for low confidence, tool failure, and timeout.
- Keep ownership and escalation routing explicit.
- Preserve reversible failure modes for safe rollback.
